Drop In Stop By December Farewell Party Invitation

Big Deals! Drop In Stop By December Farewell Party Invitation – Retirement Party Invitations This item is trending! Drop In Stop By December Farewell Party Invitation help you save during this period Drop In Stop By December Farewell Party Invitation See more about itThis cute, illustrated December drop-in farewell party invitation is perfect for celebrating someone special to you as they embark on a new adventure! Featuring original line art of a decorated holiday cottage house surrounded by cute deer and Christmas decorations, this invitation is warm and welcoming! Perfect for gatherings during the holiday season, all you have to do is just add your own celebration details for the perfect custom house party invitation! Made for a drop-in style gathering, this could also be used for retirement parties, birthdays, pot luck groups, book clubs, graduations, or housewarming parties where you want to invite guests to just stop by for a quick visit! Make it your own by editing the customizable text to say whatever you like. (Planning tip: Customize the time you want guests to arrive right on the invitations to avoid everyone arriving at the same time!) Instant downloads are also available for quick, hassle free sending to friends, family, and acquaintances! Other cottage styles available in the Drop In Farewell Party Invitation Collection. Illustrated by Tiffany Duffy. Price:$2.09
